OL,3,CDriver guilty of murdering teen mowed
OL,4,Cdown by car in Sheffield
OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurdering a 16-year-old boy who was
OL,8,Fmowed down on a pavement in Sheffield.
OL,10,FAbdullah Yaser Abdullah Taleb was
OL,11,Fkilled when he was struck by an Audi
OL,12,Fdriven by Zulkernain Ahmed on June 4
OL,13,Flast year, Sheffield Crown Court heard.
OL,15,FJurors were shown graphic video
OL,16,Ffootage of the vehicle moving to the
OL,17,Fwrong side of the road, hitting an e-
OL,18,Fbike rider called La'rome Divers,
OL,19,Fknocking him over a hedge.
