OL,3,CDriver guilty of murdering teen mowed
OL,4,Cdown by car in Sheffield
OL,6,FThe car then continued forward,
OL,7,Fhitting the teenager, also known as
OL,8,FAbdullah Yaser Abdullah Al-Yazidi, who
OL,9,Fwas seen throwing and catching a water
OL,10,Fbottle as he walked along the pavement
OL,11,Fon Staniforth Road.
OL,13,FHe was thrown in the air by the impact.
OL,15,FZulkernain Ahmed, 21, was found guilty
OL,16,Fof murder at Sheffield Crown Court.
OL,18,FHis brother Armaan Ahmed, 27, who was
OL,19,Fa back seat passenger in the Audi, was
OL,20,Fcleared of murder but found guilty of
OL,21,Fmanslaughter by the jury.
