OL,3,CDriver guilty of murdering teen mowed
OL,4,Cdown by car in Sheffield
OL,6,FAnother Ahmed brother, Zain, was the
OL,7,Ffront seat passenger, but has not yet
OL,8,Fbeen traced by police.
OL,10,FProsecutors said Zulkernain Ahmed set
OL,11,Fout to target Mr Divers, who was
OL,12,Friding in the Darnall area of
OL,13,FSheffield, with two others - one on a
OL,14,Fmoped and the other on another e-bike.
OL,16,FMr Divers, who refused to make a
OL,17,Fstatement to police, was seriously
OL,18,Finjured in the incident, the court
OL,19,Fheard.
