OL,3,CDriver guilty of murdering teen mowed
OL,4,Cdown by car in Sheffield
OL,6,FThe jury was told by prosecutors that
OL,7,FAbdullah was "in the wrong place at
OL,8,Fthe wrong time" and that the car was
OL,9,Fused as a "weapon".
OL,11,FThe defendants were out looking for Mr
OL,12,FDivers in relation to a dispute about
OL,13,Fe-bikes.
OL,15,FWhen he gave evidence in the trial,
OL,16,FZulkernain Ahmed said he was looking
OL,17,Ffor Mr Divers because he was worried
OL,18,Fhe was a threat to his family, and
OL,19,Fspotted him riding on Staniforth Road.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
