OL,3,CDriver guilty of murdering teen mowed
OL,4,Cdown by car in Sheffield
OL,6,FThe defendant, who admitted taking a
OL,7,Fbaseball bat with him, told the jury
OL,8,Fhe only wanted to talk to Mr Divers
OL,9,Fbut "at the last second I got scared
OL,10,Fand panicked" and decided to "give him
OL,11,Fa nudge".
OL,13,FHe told the jury: "It was not my
OL,14,Fintention for anything like this to
OL,15,Fhappen to (Abdullah) or to anyone."
OL,17,FArmaan Ahmed told police he went with
OL,18,Fhis brother for a meeting about a
OL,19,Fbike, and he was there to "make sure
OL,20,Fhe was safe".
