OL,3,CDriver guilty of murdering teen mowed
OL,4,Cdown by car in Sheffield
OL,6,FShortly after the incident, relatives
OL,7,Fand friends of the teenager said he
OL,8,Fwas devoted to his family and would
OL,9,F"light up their faces with a big
OL,10,Fsmile".
OL,12,FHe arrived in the UK from Yemen two or
OL,13,Fthree months before the tragedy, and
OL,14,Fhad devoted himself to learning
OL,15,FEnglish ahead of starting at college
OL,16,Fin September.
OL,18,FOne family member said Abdullah had
OL,19,Fbeen in his shop on Staniforth Road
OL,20,Fjust before the crash.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
