OL,3,CDriver guilty of murdering teen mowed
OL,4,Cdown by car in Sheffield
OL,6,FSaleh Alsirkal said: "His dad brought
OL,7,Fhim over to change his life, to get a
OL,8,Fbetter future for his son, but this
OL,9,Fhas happened and destroyed everything."
OL,11,FZulkernain Ahmed, of Locke Drive,
OL,12,FDarnall, was also found guilty of
OL,13,Fcausing e-bike rider La'rome Divers
OL,14,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent and
OL,15,Fattempting to cause the other two
OL,16,Friders - who have never been
OL,17,Fidentified - grievous bodily harm with
OL,18,Fintent.
